media.ext_alt_text:
"Through worlds"

This is a story about the universe, about life, about love, about aspiration.

Here and now on the planet Kasio2450, a cute girl Sirenia confesses her love to a Dragon. Look how her heart shines, the power of her love is immeasurable. And she is ready to give her heart, her world, her galaxy for the sake of her lover!

Years earlier, it became impossible to live on planet Earth. Scientists around the world were looking for a new planet suitable for human habitation. In 2450, the great scientist and astronaut Kasio Benj finally found this very planet. But it was inhabited. Intelligent creatures Dragons inhabited the planet, which was named Kasio2450 in honor of the scientist. Both humans and dragons had to put up with the coexistence of each other on the same planet. And after many years, the harmony of life finally came.

What awaits a little and fragile  girl Sirenia? Will the Dragon be able to accept her most precious wealth - life?
Sirenia has no other way...
